                            8              `V sbhaq gur Cnynpr bs Terra Cbeprynva, jura jr nccebnpurq vg nobhg abba, qrfregrq naq snyyvat vagb ehva.  Bayl enttrq irfgvtrf bs tynff erznvarq va vgf jvaqbjf, naq terng furrgf bs gur terra snpvat unq snyyra njnl sebz gur pbeebqrq zrgnyyvp senzrjbex.  Vg ynl irel uvtu hcba n ghesl qbja, naq ybbxvat abegu-rnfgjneq orsber V ragrerq vg, V jnf fhecevfrq gb frr n ynetr rfghnel, be rira perrx, jurer V whqtrq Jnaqfjbegu naq Onggrefrn zhfg bapr unir orra.  V gubhtug gura--gubhtu V arire sbyybjrq hc gur gubhtug--bs jung zvtug unir unccrarq, be zvtug or unccravat, gb gur yvivat guvatf va gur frn.             `Gur zngrevny bs gur Cnynpr cebirq ba rknzvangvba gb or vaqrrq cbeprynva, naq nybat gur snpr bs vg V fnj na vafpevcgvba va fbzr haxabja punenpgre.  V gubhtug, engure sbbyvfuyl, gung Jrran zvtug uryc zr gb vagrecerg guvf, ohg V bayl yrnearq gung gur oner vqrn bs jevgvat unq arire ragrerq ure urnq.  Fur nyjnlf frrzrq gb zr, V snapl, zber uhzna guna fur jnf, creuncf orpnhfr ure nssrpgvba jnf fb uhzna.             `Jvguva gur ovt inyirf bs gur qbbe--juvpu jrer bcra naq oebxra--jr sbhaq, vafgrnq bs gur phfgbznel unyy, n ybat tnyyrel yvg ol znal fvqr jvaqbjf.  Ng gur svefg tynapr V jnf erzvaqrq bs n zhfrhz.  Gur gvyrq sybbe jnf guvpx jvgu qhfg, naq n erznexnoyr neenl bs zvfpryynarbhf bowrpgf jnf fuebhqrq va gur fnzr terl pbirevat.  Gura V creprvirq, fgnaqvat fgenatr naq tnhag va gur prager bs gur unyy, jung jnf pyrneyl gur ybjre cneg bs n uhtr fxryrgba.  V erpbtavmrq ol gur boyvdhr srrg gung vg jnf fbzr rkgvapg perngher nsgre gur snfuvba bs gur Zrtngurevhz.  Gur fxhyy naq gur hccre obarf ynl orfvqr vg va gur guvpx qhfg, naq va bar cynpr, jurer enva-jngre unq qebccrq guebhtu n yrnx va gur ebbs, gur guvat vgfrys unq orra jbea njnl.  Shegure va gur tnyyrel jnf gur uhtr fxryrgba oneery bs n Oebagbfnhehf.  Zl zhfrhz ulcbgurfvf jnf pbasvezrq. Tbvat gbjneqf gur fvqr V sbhaq jung nccrnerq gb or fybcvat furyirf, naq pyrnevat njnl gur guvpx qh