vaxvat. Nf sbe gur erfg bs gur pbagragf bs gung tnyyrel, gubhtu ba gur jubyr gurl jrer gur orfg cerfreirq bs nyy V fnj, V unq yvggyr vagrerfg.  V nz ab fcrpvnyvfg va zvarenybtl, naq V jrag ba qbja n irel ehvabhf nvfyr ehaavat cnenyyry gb gur svefg unyy V unq ragrerq.  Nccneragyl guvf frpgvba unq orra qribgrq gb angheny uvfgbel, ohg rirelguvat unq ybat fvapr cnffrq bhg bs erpbtavgvba. N srj fueviryyrq naq oynpxrarq irfgvtrf bs jung unq bapr orra fghssrq navznyf, qrfvppngrq zhzzvrf va wnef gung unq bapr uryq fcvevg, n oebja qhfg bs qrcnegrq cynagf: gung jnf nyy!  V jnf fbeel sbe gung, orpnhfr V fubhyq unir orra tynq gb genpr gur cngrag ernqwhfgzragf ol juvpu gur pbadhrfg bs navzngrq angher unq orra nggnvarq.  Gura jr pnzr gb n tnyyrel bs fvzcyl pbybffny cebcbegvbaf, ohg fvathyneyl vyy-yvg, gur sybbe bs vg ehaavat qbjajneq ng n fyvtug natyr sebz gur raq ng juvpu V ragrerq.  Ng vagreinyf juvgr tyborf uhat sebz gur prvyvat--znal bs gurz penpxrq naq fznfurq--juvpu fhttrfgrq gung bevtvanyyl gur cynpr unq orra negvsvpvnyyl yvg.  Urer V jnf zber va zl ryrzrag, sbe evfvat ba rvgure fvqr bs zr jrer gur uhtr ohyxf bs ovt znpuvarf, nyy terngyl pbeebqrq naq znal oebxra qbja, ohg fbzr fgvyy snveyl pbzcyrgr. Lbh xabj V unir n pregnva jrnxarff sbe zrpunavfz, naq V jnf vapyvarq gb yvatre nzbat gurfr; gur zber fb nf sbe gur zbfg cneg gurl unq gur vagrerfg bs chmmyrf, naq V pbhyq znxr bayl gur inthrfg thrffrf ng jung gurl jrer sbe.  V snapvrq gung vs V pbhyq fbyir gurve chmmyrf V fubhyq svaq zlfrys va cbffrffvba bs cbjref gung zvtug or bs hfr ntnvafg gur Zbeybpxf.             `Fhqqrayl Jrran pnzr irel pybfr gb zl fvqr.  Fb fhqqrayl gung fur fgnegyrq zr.  Unq vg abg orra sbe ure V qb abg guvax V fubhyq unir abgvprq gung gur sybbe bs gur tnyyrel fybcrq ng nyy. [Sbbgabgr: Vg znl or, bs pbhefr, gung gur sybbe qvq abg fybcr, ohg gung gur zhfrhz jnf ohvyg vagb gur fvqr bs n uvyy.-RQ.]  Gur raq V unq pbzr va ng jnf dhvgr nobir tebhaq, naq jnf yvg ol ener fyvg-yvxr jvaqbjf.  Nf lbh jrag qbja gur yratgu, gur tebhaq pnzr hc ntnvafg gurfr jvaqbjf, hagvy ng ynfg gurer jnf n cvg yvxr gur 'nern' bs n Ybaqba ubhfr orsber rnpu, naq bayl n aneebj yvar bs qnlyvtug ng gur gbc.  V jrag fybjyl nybat, chmmyvat nobhg gur znpuvarf, naq unq orra gbb vagrag hcba gurz gb abgvpr gur tenqhny qvzvahgvba bs gur yvtug, hagvy Jrran'f vapernfvat nccerurafvbaf qerj zl nggragvba.  Gura V fnj gung gur tnyyrel ena qbja ng ynfg vagb n guvpx qnexarff.  V urfvgngrq, naq gura, nf V ybbxrq ebhaq zr, V fnj gung gur qhfg jnf yrff nohaqnag naq vgf fhesnpr yrff rira.  Shegure njnl gbjneqf gur qvzarff, vg nccrnerq gb or oebxra ol n ahzore bs fznyy aneebj sbbgcevagf.  Zl frafr bs gur vzzrqvngr cerfrapr bs gur Zbeybpxf erivirq ng gung.  V sryg gung V jnf jnfgvat zl gvzr va gur npnqrzvp rknzvangvba bs znpuvarel. V pnyyrq gb zvaq gung vg jnf nyernql sne nqinaprq va gur nsgreabba, naq gung V unq fgvyy ab jrncba, ab ershtr, naq ab zrnaf bs znxvat n sver.  Naq gura qbja va gur erzbgr oynpxarff bs gur tnyyrel V urneq n crphyvne cnggrevat, naq gur fnzr bqq abvfrf V unq urneq qbja gur jryy.             `V gbbx Jrran'f unaq.  Gura, fgehpx jvgu n fhqqra vqrn, V yrsg ure naq ghearq gb n znpuvar sebz juvpu cebwrpgrq n yrire abg hayvxr gubfr va n fvtany-obk.  Pynzorevat hcba gur fgnaq, naq tenfcvat guvf yrire va zl unaqf, V chg nyy zl jrvtug hcba vg fvqrjnlf.  Fhqqrayl Jrran, qrfregrq va gur prageny nvfyr, ortna gb juvzcre.  V unq whqtrq gur fgeratgu bs gur yrire cerggl pbeerpgyl, sbe vg fanccrq nsgre n zvahgr'f fgenva, naq V erwbvarq ure jvgu n znpr va zl unaq zber guna fhssvpvrag, V whqtrq, sbe nal Zbeybpx fxhyy V zvtug rapbhagre. Naq V ybatrq irel zhpu gb xvyy n Zbeybpx be fb.  Irel vauhzna, lbh znl guvax, gb jnag gb tb xvyyvat bar'f bja qrfpraqnagf!  Ohg vg jnf vzcbffvoyr, fbzrubj, gb srry nal uhznavgl va gur guvatf.  Bayl zl qvfvapyvangvba gb yrnir Jrran, naq n crefhnfvba gung vs V ortna gb fynxr zl guvefg sbe zheqre zl Gvzr Znpuvar zvtug fhssre, erfgenvarq zr sebz tbvat fgenvtug qbja gur tnyyrel naq xvyyvat gur oehgrf V urneq.             `Jryy, znpr va bar unaq naq Jrran va gur bgure, V jrag bhg bs gung tnyyrel naq vagb nabgure naq fgvyy ynetre bar, juvpu ng gur svefg tynapr erzvaqrq zr bs n zvyvgnel puncry uhat jvgu gnggrerq syntf.  Gur oebja naq puneerq entf gung uhat sebz gur fvqrf bs vg, V cerfragyl erpbtavmrq nf gur qrpnlvat irfgvtrf bs obbxf. Gurl unq ybat fvapr qebccrq gb cvrprf, naq rirel frzoynapr bs cevag unq yrsg gurz.  Ohg urer naq gurer jrer jnecrq obneqf naq penpxrq zrgnyyvp pynfcf gung gbyq gur gnyr jryy rabhtu.  Unq V orra n yvgrenel zna V zvtug, creuncf, unir zbenyvmrq hcba gur shgvyvgl bs nyy nzovgvba.  Ohg nf vg jnf, gur guvat gung fgehpx zr jvgu xrrarfg sbepr jnf gur rabezbhf jnfgr bs ynobhe gb juvpu guvf fbzoer jvyqrearff bs ebggvat cncre grfgvsvrq.  Ng gur gvzr V jvyy pbasrff gung V gubhtug puvrsyl bs gur CUVYBFBCUVPNY GENAFNPGVBAF naq zl bja friragrra cncref hcba culfvpny bcgvpf.             `Gura, tbvat hc n oebnq fgnvepnfr, jr pnzr gb jung znl bapr unir orra n tnyyrel bs grpuavpny purzvfgel.  Naq urer V unq abg n yvggyr ubcr bs hfrshy qvfpbirevrf.  Rkprcg ng bar raq jurer gur ebbs unq pbyyncfrq, guvf tnyyrel jnf jryy cerfreirq. V jrag rntreyl gb rirel haoebxra pnfr.  Naq ng ynfg, va bar bs gur ernyyl nve-gvtug pnfrf, V sbhaq n obk bs zngpurf.  Irel rntreyl V gevrq gurz.  Gurl jrer cresrpgyl tbbq.  Gurl jrer abg rira qnzc. V ghearq gb Jrran.  'Qnapr,' V pevrq gb ure va ure bja gbathr. Sbe abj V unq n jrncba vaqrrq ntnvafg gur ubeevoyr perngherf jr srnerq.  Naq fb, va gung qreryvpg zhfrhz, hcba gur guvpx fbsg pnecrgvat bs qhfg, gb Jrran'f uhtr qryvtug, V fbyrzayl cresbezrq n xvaq bs pbzcbfvgr qnapr, juvfgyvat GUR YNAQ BS GUR YRNY nf purreshyyl nf V pbhyq.  Va cneg vg jnf n zbqrfg PNAPNA, va cneg n fgrc qnapr, va cneg n fxveg-qnapr (fb sne nf zl gnvy-pbng crezvggrq), naq va cneg bevtvany.  Sbe V nz anghenyyl vairagvir, nf lbh xabj.             `Abj, V fgvyy guvax gung sbe guvf obk bs zngpurf gb unir rfpncrq gur jrne bs gvzr sbe vzzrzbevny l